MILESTONE for version 1.0:

- ESC ==> exit and go to Menu... Always!
- camera only above ground
- Put some effects in the end of the game when "selecting" the balls
- It's possible (and easy) to win against Minmax. Let it better.
- Put some information while playing in UI3d, like players' names
- Status bar to display messsages to user
- Play without a selected player => open configuration menu
- UI3d == default UI

